00:06:39.660 --> 00:06:40.980
Song Zhizhi.

00:06:41.620 --> 00:06:42.700
Song Zhizhi.

00:06:45.300 --> 00:06:45.860
Wenhan,

00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:47.220
you worked so hard

00:06:47.220 --> 00:06:48.900
all these years

