I thought it was because of the milk.

00:08:22.620 --> 00:08:23.700
But how could this happen?

00:08:26.380 --> 00:08:27.860
The results for the hair sample
you asked me to test

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:28.740
are also out.

00:08:30.980 --> 00:08:32.220
The results show

00:08:34.220 --> 00:08:36.460
Nie Xiaofei is not related to Yi Wenhan

00:08:36.540 --> 00:08:37.500
or Nie Wenzhi.

